<reference id="linkpool" xml:lang="en-us">
<title><xmlelement>linkpool</xmlelement></title>
<shortdesc>The <xmlelement>linkpool</xmlelement> element defines
a group of links that have common characteristics, such as type or
audience or source. When links are in <xmlelement>related-links</xmlelement> or <xmlelement>linkpool</xmlelement>
elements, the organization of links on final output is determined
by the output process, not by the order that the links actually occur
in the DITA topic.</shortdesc>
